videos.headline: Miami celebrates after forcing fumble
videos.description: Trajan Bandy's fumble recovery sparks a celebration that ends with the Hurricanes posing for the camera with their turnover chain.

videos.headline: Miami punt return TD stands after lengthy review
videos.description: DeeJay Dallas' 65-yard punt return TD stands after a targeting flag was reviewed.

videos.headline: Homer shows burst on TD run
videos.description: Travis Homer zooms 64 yards for an electric touchdown run to give Miami a 14-point lead in the third quarter.
